<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4271703>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Geographical distribution of Hyphessobrycon frickei Guimarães, Brito, Bragança, Katz & Ottoni sp. nov. and H. geryi Guimarães, Brito, Bragança, Katz & Ottoni sp. nov. Red star denotes holotype and blue circle denotes paratypes of H. frickei Guimarães, Brito, Bragança, Katz & Ottoni sp. nov. whereas white star denotes holotype and the black circles denote paratypes of H. geryi Guimarães, Brito, Bragança, Katz & Ottoni sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4271703/files/figure.png" ;
